			* rights are maximal
				* differently phrased: partial violation of right is violation of right
				* by type of partial violation
					* a right includes the right to ask for and provide help to exercise the right
						* a right includes the right to exercise the right in groups, with cooperation
					* a right includes the right to exercise the right secretly, anonimously
					* a right includes the right to exercise the right  without attached obligation or (negative discrimination as consequence)
				* i have the feeling that this phrasing is not precise enough
					* but this imprecision is only technical, it does not make the meaning incorrect
